text: FOP's compliance page (http://xmlgraphics.apache.org/fop/compliance.html) still refers to XSL-FO 1.0 whereas the project set its goal to reach XSL-FO 1.1 compliance several years ago by now. The text needs to be refreshed, the links to the specification updated and entries for XSL-FO 1.1 elements must be added in the compliance tables.
